com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query.graph

Class GraphCentricQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query.BaseQuery
      • com.thinkaurelius.titan.graphdb.query.graph.GraphCentricQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElementQuery<TitanElement,JointIndexQuery>, ProfileObservable, Query

    public class GraphCentricQuery
extends BaseQuery
implements ElementQuery<TitanElement,JointIndexQuery>, ProfileObservable
    An executable ElementQuery for TitanGraphQuery. This query contains the condition, and only one sub-query JointIndexQuery. It also maintains the ordering for the query result which is needed by the QueryProcessor to correctly order the result.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
